WEBVTT

00:02:57.163 --> 00:03:00.194
that obscured its meaning
until relatively recently.

00:03:01.031 --> 00:03:03.357
Nature provided no card catalog
for geologists --

00:03:03.381 --> 00:03:05.094
this would have to be invented.

00:03:06.079 --> 00:03:09.710
Five thousand years after the Sumerians
learned to record their thoughts

00:03:09.734 --> 00:03:10.886
on clay tablets,

00:03:10.910 --> 00:03:13.993
the Earth's volumes remained
inscrutable to humans.

00:03:14.495 --> 00:03:16.959
We were geologically illiterate,

00:03:17.637 --> 00:03:20.819
unaware of the antiquity
of our own planet

00:03:20.843 --> 00:03:22.352
and ignorant of our connection

00:03:22.376 --> 00:03:23.573
to deep time.

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:28.216
It wasn't until the turn
of the 19th century

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:30.636
that our blinders were removed,